<h2 id="3-why-are-averages-important">3. Why are averages important?</h2>
<p><a href="https://postimg.cc/H8M6fKLp">&lt;img src=â€https://i.postimg.cc/nrRNQfbQ/22.pngâ€width=â€500pxâ€ title=â€source: imgur.comâ€ /&gt;</a></p>
